metadata.name: Shroomshifter
metadata.description:
An alchemical accident.. or perhaps a product of nature... or maybe just a very convincing hallucination.. 

Either way, this is not a localized phenomenon. 
There is something taking place throughout the entire Cluster-verse!

Unique species of fungal organisms are merging with shapeshifters of all sorts.

The mainlanders are saying this is a natural course of evolution.. but the elders say there is something disturbing the balance of Nature.
